				<section class="has_ae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-eeb7a27 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default ae-bg-gallery-type-default" data-id="eeb7a27" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-e284510 ae-bg-gallery-type-default" data-id="e284510" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-8bc4a1d elementor-widget elementor-widget-theme-post-title elementor-page-title elementor-widget-heading" data-id="8bc4a1d" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="theme-post-title.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h1 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">BURNIN&#8217; UP &#8211; Saturday BBQ Buffet</h1>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-de56194 elementor-widget elementor-widget-theme-post-content" data-id="de56194" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="theme-post-content.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Discover Saturday nights at Magic Lounge as vibrant energy returns with Burnin’ Up – a BBQ buffet where every dish comes alive with smoky flavors and ocean breeze.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Indulge in aromatic grilled selections, fresh seafood, succulent meats, and refined desserts. A lively feast filled with music and laughter sets the tone for radiant summer evenings.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">🔥Buffet starts from VND 995,000 nett/adult and VND 695,000 nett/child, inclusive of one soft drink or local beer.<br>🦞Enhance your experience with a premium upgrade featuring half grilled lobster, served at the table, at VND 1,195,000 nett/adult.<br>🕰 18:30 – 21:30 | Every Saturday (30/5 – 11/7, excluding 4/7)<br>📜View menu in details: <a href="https://tmshotel.vn/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Saturday-BBQ-Buffet.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">MENU</a></p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">🌟Early Bird Offer: enjoy 10% off for the first 20 booking guests</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Reserve your table for a memorable Saturday night!</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Location: Magic Lounge – 25th floor TMS Hotel Da Nang Beach</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For enquiries and reservations, please contact:</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Phone: +84 236 3755 999</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Email: reservation-dn@tmshotel.vn</p>
				</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
